node.text:
Holiday shoppin’ #bourbon style 🎁🥃! Our own Seth Thompson is here to guide you through the @buffalotracedistillery Gift Shop experience, a brand new Covid safe bourbon haven! Curbside pickup is available. Check out their website for the goods: http://buffalotrace.me/bourbonreview 

Here’s to a safe and happy holiday🎁🥃
.
.
.
#bourbon #bourbonwhiskey #buffalotracedistillery #holidayseason #holidayshopping  #cigar #yeti #eaglerare #buffalotrace #kentucky #kentuckybourbon #bourboncountry

node.text:
🥃America’s Best Bourbon Bars🥃
We absolutely love kicking off #nationalbourbonheritagemonth by saluting the very best of the best Bourbon destinations across the nation! Here’s to a month long celebration of our native spirit and cheers to all the fantastic Bourbon bars out there! Full list on our bio link. Five regions of Bourbon bliss🤩🥃 Special thanks to our partner @buffalotracedistillery for their support!
📸 @thecrunkletoncharlotte
.
.
#bourbon #bourboncountry #buffalotrace #buffalotracedistillery #bestbourbonbars #bestbournbonbars21 #whiskey

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Bourbon Review on September 01, 2021. May be an image of ‎text that says '‎م ﷺ oldforester It's our birthday- and we love celebrating our annual release of Old Forester Birthday Bourbon. Due to safety concerns, we have decided to hand out tickets to those in line for Birthday Bourbon 2021. This means all bottles for the September 2nd Distillery release have been committed.
